{"sn12.48:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.48 ","sn12.48:0.2":"5. Gahapativagga ","sn12.48:0.3":"Lokayatikasutta ","sn12.48:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn12.48:1.2":"Atha kho lokayatiko brahmano yena bhagava …pe… ","sn12.48:1.3":"ekamantam nisinno kho lokayatiko brahmano bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn12.48:2.1":"“Kim nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamatthi”ti? ","sn12.48:2.2":"“‘Sabbamatthi’ti kho, brahmana, jetthametam lokayatam”. ","sn12.48:3.1":"“Kim pana, bho gotama, sabbam natthi”ti? ","sn12.48:3.2":"“‘Sabbam natthi’ti kho, brahmana, dutiyametam lokayatam”. ","sn12.48:4.1":"“Kim nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamekattan”ti? ","sn12.48:4.2":"“‘Sabbamekattan’ti kho, brahmana, tatiyametam lokayatam”. ","sn12.48:5.1":"“Kim pana, bho gotama, sabbam puthuttan”ti? ","sn12.48:5.2":"“‘Sabbam puthuttan’ti kho, brahmana, catutthametam lokayatam. ","sn12.48:6.1":"Ete te, brahmana, ubho ante anupagamma majjhena tathagato dhammam deseti: ","sn12.48:6.2":"‘avijjapaccaya sankhara; ","sn12.48:6.3":"sankharapaccaya vinnanam …pe… ","sn12.48:6.4":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.48:6.5":"Avijjaya tveva asesaviraganirodha sankharanirodho; ","sn12.48:6.6":"sankharanirodha vinnananirodho …pe… ","sn12.48:6.7":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti’”ti. ","sn12.48:7.1":"Evam vutte, lokayatiko brahmano bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn12.48:7.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama …pe… ","sn12.48:7.3":"ajjatagge panupetam saranam gatan”ti. ","sn12.48:7.4":"Atthamam. "}